SOP: Policy Tuning & Continuous Improvement (Reduce Noise, Improve Signal)
Purpose
Continuously refine DLP to reduce false positives and align enforcement with real workflows. 
Inputs
•	Alert outcomes (FP/TP), override patterns, noisy rules, impacted workflows 
Process
1.	Post Alert Review
o	Did the policy work as intended? 
o	Was the rule too broad?
o	Were notifications appropriate? 
2.	Tuning Actions
o	Refine detection conditions 
o	Narrow/expand scope 
o	Adjust actions (warn vs block) 
o	Adjust alert thresholds (single vs aggregate) 
3.	Re validate
o	Use simulation again after meaningful changes 
4.	Document
o	Update the policy record with what changed and why (recommended template)
Output
•	Versioned tuning log + reduced noise and improved detection accuracy over time. 
